@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_iecyvb(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.abs(wp.cos(v0 + 0.31)) - wp.abs(wp.abs(v0 + 0.03)))
    tmp = ((tmp / (v2 + 0.29 - v1 + 0.41)) + wp.exp(wp.sin(v0 + 0.94)))
    v1 = v2
    v0 = (((v1 + 0.28 / v0 + 0.29) + wp.cos(tmp + 0.02)) - (v1 + 0.20))
    tmp = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
